{"TopicId":186155,"ForumId":69,"TopicTitle":"Difficulty setting limits","CreatedByName":"kyoden","CreatedById":159876,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-07-07T18:42:02Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"kyoden","CreatedById":159876,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-07-07T18:42:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow does one fix this problem of using the sliders to set precise numbers?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI am \u003Cem\u003Etrying\u003C/em\u003E to set the Angle Limit to 0 and 90, but it takes 15 minutes for the game to get it right.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis I have tried:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNew mice, including wired, wireless.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nChanging resolution of the game ( I usually play at 2560x1440 )\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMoving the window around trying again.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTrying key modifiers like Alt, Ctrl, Shift and Caps Lock\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRunning stock, completely stock unmodded brand new fresh install of 1.7.2 with both DLC\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022JK7uNOe.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022150.57\u0022 height=\u0022399\u0022 width=\u0022265\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/JK7uNOe.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Geonovast","CreatedById":179753,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-07-07T18:43:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou wait for 1.7.3\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022196576\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed9555788157\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/186100-ksp-loading-preview-improvements-to-paw-sliders/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:193px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kyoden","Create